metadata.description: “Sleepless” is the birth child of “Dutch Melrose”. The song that started everything for me. It’s about the 2am thoughts that keep you up at night when you first fall in love. The overwhelming feeling that there’s no turning back. That even if you tried, you couldn’t shake the feeling that you’re in too deep. Nostalgic, effortless, and hypnotizing. “Sleepless” is the all too familiar feeling when we decide to let our walls down and realize that the other person we love has become our everything.
